/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 730.0 Tm (A transparent way to speak with a receptionist or assistant that treats them as a person) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 716.0 Tm (and a potential ally, asks for help directly, and never uses deception to get past them.) Tj
/F2 13 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 692.0 Tm (Learning objectives) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.0 675.0 Tm (- Greet the gatekeeper and ask for help directly) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 661.0 Tm (- Be transparent about who you are and why you called) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 647.0 Tm (- Accept their answer gracefully, including no) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 633.0 Tm (- Leave a professional impression even if you do not get through) Tj
/F2 13 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 613.0 Tm (Principles) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.0 596.0 Tm (- Be honest: never pretend to be a customer, a friend, or a returning caller.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 582.0 Tm (- Be brief: state who you are and what you are hoping to do in one breath.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 568.0 Tm (- Ask for guidance: gatekeepers often know the best person and the best time.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 554.0 Tm (- Be gracious: thank them regardless of the outcome.) Tj
/F2 13 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 534.0 Tm (A simple flow) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.0 517.0 Tm (1. Warm greeting and your name and company.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 503.0 Tm (2. Honest reason: "I am hoping to reach whoever looks after [area] - am I in the) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 489.0 Tm (right place?") Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 475.0 Tm (3. If asked what it is about, give a plain one-line answer.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 461.0 Tm (4. If it is not a good time, ask when would be better and thank them.) Tj
/F2 13 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 441.0 Tm (Worked example) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 424.0 Tm ("Hi, this is Sam with Northlight - I am probably not who you were expecting today. I am) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 410.0 Tm (trying to reach whoever looks after driver scheduling, and I am guessing you would know) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 396.0 Tm (better than I would. Who should I be speaking with, and is there a good time to catch) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 382.0 Tm (them?") Tj
/F2 13 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 358.0 Tm (Safe-practice note) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 341.0 Tm (Do not use tricks, false urgency, or claims of an existing relationship to get past a) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 327.0 Tm (gatekeeper. Honesty here protects your reputation and theirs. If they decline, accept it) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 313.0 Tm (politely.) Tj
